    <main id="main-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="issue-hero" style="background-image: url('assets/images/placeholder-hero.jpg');">
            <div class="issue-hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-hero-content">
                    <h1>Council on Environmental Quality</h1>
                    <p class="issue-hero-description">Leading the charge for environmental protection, climate action, and sustainable dreamhouses for generations to come.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Overview Section -->
        <section class="issue-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-overview-content">
                    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
                    <p>The Council on Environmental Quality (CEQ) coordinates federal environmental efforts and works closely with agencies and other Executive Office components to develop environmental and energy policies and initiatives. CEQ was established by the National Environmental Policy Act and serves as the principal advisor to the President on environmental policy.</p>
                    <p>We work to ensure that environmental considerations are integrated into all federal decision-making, promoting sustainable practices, protecting natural resources, and addressing the urgent challenge of climate change. From green dreamhouse initiatives to renewable energy investments, CEQ helps shape policies that protect our planet for future generations of dolls.</p>
                    <p>Our council oversees the environmental review process for federal actions, coordinates climate change initiatives, promotes environmental justice, and ensures that the voices of all doll communities are heard in environmental decision-making. We believe that environmental protection and economic prosperity go hand in hand.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Key Initiatives -->
        <section class="initiatives-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Key Focus Areas</h2>
                <div class="initiatives-grid">
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🌍</span>
                        <h3>Climate Action</h3>
                        <p>Developing comprehensive strategies to combat climate change, reduce emissions, and build resilience in doll communities.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🏡</span>
                        <h3>Green Dreamhouses</h3>
                        <p>Promoting sustainable building practices, energy efficiency, and eco-friendly design in dreamhouse construction nationwide.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">♻️</span>
                        <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                        <p>Advancing circular economy principles, waste reduction, and sustainable consumption patterns across all sectors.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">⚡</span>
                        <h3>Clean Energy</h3>
                        <p>Accelerating the transition to renewable energy sources and supporting innovation in clean energy technologies.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🌳</span>
                        <h3>Conservation</h3>
                        <p>Protecting natural landscapes, preserving biodiversity, and ensuring access to beautiful outdoor spaces for all dolls.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">⚖️</span>
                        <h3>Environmental Justice</h3>
                        <p>Ensuring that all doll communities, especially historically marginalized ones, benefit from environmental protections.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Leadership Section -->
        <section class="priority-areas-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Leadership</h2>
                <div class="priority-block">
                    <h3>Chair of the Council</h3>
                    <p>The Chair of the Council on Environmental Quality is appointed by the President and confirmed by the Senate. The Chair leads a dedicated team of environmental policy experts and coordinates environmental initiatives across the federal government, working closely with Cabinet officials and agency leaders.</p>
                    <p>The Chair also serves as a key advisor to the President on environmental matters, ensuring that sustainability and environmental protection are central considerations in policy development across all issue areas.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="priority-block">
                    <h3>NEPA Oversight</h3>
                    <p>CEQ oversees implementation of the National Environmental Policy Act (NEPA), which requires federal agencies to assess the environmental impacts of their actions. This critical responsibility ensures that environmental considerations are integrated into federal decision-making, promoting transparency and informed choices.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

